Omniscient Reader's Viewpoint

전지적 독자 시점 , 전독시 , Jeonjijeok Dokja Sijeom , Lecteur omniscient , Lector omnisciente , ORV , Punkt Widzenia Wszechwiedzącego Czytelnika , Всеведущий читатель , دیدگاه خواننده‌ی همه‌چی‌دون , وجهة نظر القارئ العراف , อ่านชะตาวันสิ้นโลก , 全知的な読者の視点から , 全知讀者視角 , 全知读者

Description

‘This is a development that I know of.’ The moment he thought that the world had been destroyed, and a new universe had unfolded. The new life of an ordinary reader begins within the world of the novel, a novel that he alone had finished.
